# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [Unreleased]
- Initial heartbeat monitoring implementation.
- In-memory storage for heartbeat events.
- REST API endpoints for posting and retrieving heartbeats.

## [0.1.0] - 2025-09-03
### Added
- First public release.
- Go server with heartbeat API.
- Basic React UI for cardiogram visualization.
- eBPF program stub.
